<P>__{(tired)}
<D>__{i picked something up on the way.}
<C>__{gondorff}
<P>__{(sensing something)}
<D>__{lonnegan after you, too?}
<C>__{hooker}
<D>__{i don't know. haven't seen anybody.}
<C>__{gondorff}
<D>__{you never do, kid.}
<A>__{we go to hooker. he hadn't thought of that.}
